reviews.review_text: Sound Review One of those, I was there so I need to have it type of shows.  IMO this night was the better of the two.  The sound quality on this recording is better than the others.

I am on an amazing journey I am listening to every 1994 show in order, mining for gold. 

I agree; this is the best AUD source. Wonderful recording for a stadium. Traffic opened. 

Set 1 HIGHlights: Very strong performances in the first set. Ramble on Rose HITS HARD. Crowd is loving it. Loose Lucy is done just right. Killer Promised Land. 

Set 2 Highlights: Last Time out of space is always nice. Stella Blue. All songs played reasonably well in the second set, but no real standouts for me.
